body_html:
@smsrikanthreddy following up on @InsZVA's point, it seems that we need to find the build rules that add CountExtremelyRandomStats. If you look at the link below we can see the rules associate with tensorForest:
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.3/tensorflow/contrib/tensor_forest/BUILD

I attempted to add the following lines to cc_binary[name="libtensorflow.so"].
"//tensorflow/contrib/tensor_forest:v2_ops",
"//tensorflow/contrib/tensor_forest:tensor_forest_v4_kernels",
"//tensorflow/contrib/tensor_forest:tensor_forest_v4_ops_op_lib"

And then copied to /usr/local/lib. But I got the same. issue. I'll try to see what I'm doing wrong over the weekend.
